Package it.polimi.ingsw.editor

Class DevelopmentCardEdit

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.editor.DevelopmentCardEdit
public class DevelopmentCardEdit
extends java.lang.Object
This class it is used by the user to modify the development cards. Given the id of the card, the user can change the production power, the victory points, the cost.
